    <string name="dict_intro_para1">Madoka Runes (also known as Inukare Runes) are the characters that appear in the anime "Puella Magi Madoka Magica" produced by SHAFT, such as in witch barriers and magical</string>
    <string name="dict_intro_para2">The characters of Madoka Runes have a one-to-one correspondence with Latin letters (including German letters, which have 4 more than English letters) and Arabic numerals.</string>
